{"tid":246941,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"反課金人士召集區[2] 歡迎課金撚入黎挑機","createTime":"2017-05-17T11:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T11:30:01.000Z","uid":18650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"884a2a39c46c3e764975dd887748ab3cf0f3dc98","tid":246941,"uid":18650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"各位, 覺唔覺得遊戲課金係一件好on9嘅事<br />\n你用錢買黎更好裝備, 更好道具, 更多遊戲幣<br />\n換黎嘅只係虛擬嘅成功同一時嘅滿足感, 自豪感同英雄感<br />\n二黎用等級壓制對手, 根本顯示唔出你嘅實力<br />\n我本身都係一個幾入迷嘅打機人士, 不過我真係完全唔鍾意課金 , 有錢都唔課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔課金個遊戲先刺激好玩, 課金好快厭<br />\n而且屌打到課金撚時個感覺真係好撚爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢嘅話我寧願食多D好西, 去多D地方旅行, 買多D自己鍾意嘅野, 甚至過大海發下達都好, 都唔會課$1落一隻game度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c511dbbe7af44639b637750a882d21d82967b00b","tid":246941,"uid":18650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:46:27.000Z","msg":"收皮啦課金狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c20a36401e12faed890afc380726cd1a501a9bc","tid":246941,"uid":1675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"十卜鐵丁"},{"pid":"b98ecde5b83b3e08593157979eeb8671260b3576","tid":246941,"uid":82572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"等埋原樓主入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99da03459ce04fac75f9bf00cbcce4063ac725d6","tid":246941,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"係咪開錯台 原post係遊戲台"},{"pid":"ccd07583ed37ae23440dcc670ab1a9ffb6d10128","tid":246941,"uid":18650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪開錯台 原post係遊戲台</blockquote><br />\n撚埋app台班課金狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866bbe2465f6378497acd52cd0a3352f3e5